 big question to ask is what is the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bankofcanada.ca\/rates\/exchange\/currency-converter\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">current Canada\/U.S. exchange rate<\/a>? The Canadian dollar changes all the time: if you can catch the loonie on the upswing, you\u2019ll save big time. Buyers need to be ready to spring into action as they watch dollar fluctuations.<\/p>\n<h1>Other questions to ask include:<\/h1>\n<ol>\n<li>What is the cars comparable cost in Canada?<\/li>\n<li>Which vehicles have the lowest import duties and taxes? The costs are not all the same, so knowing ahead of time will help narrow your search.<\/li>\n<li>Are there any repair or modification requirements? Canada has strict safety standards for import vehicles, so be sure there aren\u2019t any hidden costs.<\/li>\n<li>Are you paying for a warranty that isn\u2019t valid in Canada?<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>If you haven\u2019t gone the cross-border route before \u2013 or even if you have, but it didn\u2019t go as smoothly as you\u2019d hoped \u2013 <a href=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/#cta-import-vehicle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">BorderBuddy can help<\/a>. Our <a href=\"https:\/\/borderbuddy.com\/about\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">customs brokers<\/a> know all the ins and outs of buying and importing fleet vehicles. Let us do the heavy lifting for you so you can get the best deal possible.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>A fleet vehicle is a car leased to a business in groups like taxis, rental cars, and police cars. To buy or not to buy a fleet vehicle in the US? That\u2019s a mighty big question. Somebody always knows somebody who got a killer deal on a fleet vehicle in the United States. But can&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":613,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"_genesis_hid